<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Jane | Pre-Seed Investor Overview</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Karla:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    :root {
      --pink: #FF6B9D;
      --coral: #FF8E72;
      --peach: #FFB88C;
      --lavender: #C89EFF;
      --mint: #7FFFDA;
      --cream: #FFF8F3;
      --dark: #2A1A3D;
      --text: #3D2952;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Karla', sans-serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.8;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    
    /* Animated gradient background */
    @keyframes gradient-shift {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }
    
    /* Hero Section with animated gradient */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #FF6B9D, #FF8E72, #C89EFF, #7FFFDA);
      background-size: 400% 400%;
      animation: gradient-shift 15s ease infinite;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: 
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 40%),
        url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="60" height="60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="5" cy="5" r="2" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)"/></svg>');
      background-size: auto, auto, 60px 60px;
      animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(5deg); }
    }
    
    .hero-content {
      text-align: center;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 2rem;
      animation: fadeInScale 1.2s ease-out;
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeInScale {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0.9);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1);
      }
    }
    
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 10rem);
      color: white;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    
    .hero .tagline {
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
      color: white;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    
    .hero .wave-divider {
      width: 600px;
      max-width: 90%;
      height: 60px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="600" height="60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M0 30 Q 150 10, 300 30 T 600 30" stroke="white" stroke-width="3" fill="none" opacity="0.8"/></svg>') center/contain no-repeat;
    }
    
    .hero .meta {
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    
    /* Container */
    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }
    
    /* Textured sections */
    section {
      padding: 5rem 0;
      position: relative;
      animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    
    /* Pink blob backgrounds */
    .blob-bg {
      position: relative;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8F3 0%, #FFE8F5 100%);
    }
    
    .blob-bg::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,107,157,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 47% 53% 61% 39% / 53% 47% 53% 47%;
      top: -100px;
      right: -100px;
      animation: blob 12s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    
    .blob-bg::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200,158,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 61% 39% 47% 53% / 47% 61% 39% 53%;
      bottom: -100px;
      left: -100px;
      animation: blob 15s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    
    @keyframes blob {
      0%, 100% { 
        transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
        border-radius: 47% 53% 61% 39% / 53% 47% 53% 47%;
      }
      33% {
        transform: translate(30px, -50px) scale(1.1);
        border-radius: 53% 47% 39% 61% / 47% 53% 61% 39%;
      }
      66% {
        transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.9);
        border-radius: 39% 61% 53% 47% / 61% 39% 47% 53%;
      }
    }
    
    /* Coral section */
    .coral-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFE8E8 0%, #FFF8F3 100%);
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .coral-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="100" height="100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="50" cy="50" r="30" fill="rgba(255,142,114,0.08)"/></svg>');
      background-size: 100px 100px;
      opacity: 0.5;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    
    section > * {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    /* Typography */
    h2 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    
    h3 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    
    .intro-text {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    .body-text {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    /* Colored text highlights */
    .highlight-pink {
      color: var(--pink);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .highlight-coral {
      color: var(--coral);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .highlight-lavender {
      color: var(--lavender);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    /* Stats cards with gradients */
    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
    }
    
    .stat-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pink) 0%, var(--coral) 100%);
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 24px;
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(255,107,157,0.3);
      transform: translateY(0);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .stat-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      right: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 60%);
      animation: shimmer 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes shimmer {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      50% { transform: translate(-30%, -30%); }
    }
    
    .stat-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(255,107,157,0.4);
    }
    
    .stat-card .number {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    }
    
    .stat-card .label {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    
    /* Callout boxes */
    .callout {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8F3 0%, white 100%);
      border-left: 6px solid var(--pink);
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    
    .callout.lavender {
      border-left-color: var(--lavender);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F5F0FF 0%, white 100%);
    }
    
    /* List styling */
    .styled-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    
    .styled-list li {
      padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem 1.2rem 3.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      position: relative;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .styled-list li:hover {
      transform: translateX(8px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(255,107,157,0.2);
    }
    
    .styled-list li::before {
      content: '✦';
      position: absolute;
      left: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--pink);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    /* Flow diagram with colorful steps */
    .flow-diagram {
      margin: 4rem 0;
      padding: 3rem;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    
    .flow-step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .flow-step:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    .flow-step::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 32px;
      top: 70px;
      width: 4px;
      height: calc(100% + 3rem);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--pink) 0%, var(--coral) 50%, var(--lavender) 100%);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    
    .flow-step:last-child::after {
      display: none;
    }
    
    .step-number {
      width: 65px;
      height: 65px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pink) 0%, var(--coral) 100%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-right: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255,107,157,0.4);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .flow-step:nth-child(2) .step-number {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--coral) 0%, var(--peach) 100%);
    }
    
    .flow-step:nth-child(3) .step-number {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--lavender) 0%, var(--pink) 100%);
    }
    
    .flow-step:nth-child(4) .step-number {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--mint) 0%, var(--lavender) 100%);
    }
    
    .step-content h4 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--dark);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .step-content p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    
    /* Tracks grid - colorful pills */
    .tracks-container {
      margin: 3rem 0;
    }
    
    .tracks-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .track-pill {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: white;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    
    .track-pill:nth-child(1) {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B9D 0%, #FF8E72 100%);
    }
    
    .track-pill:nth-child(2) {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C89EFF 0%, #FF6B9D 100%);
    }
    
    .track-pill:nth-child(3) {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFB88C 0%, #FF8E72 100%);
    }
    
    .track-pill:nth-child(4) {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7FFFDA 0%, #C89EFF 100%);
    }
    
    .track-pill:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }
    
    /* Membership CTA */
    .membership-banner {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark) 0%, #4A2D6E 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 3rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 3rem 0;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(42,26,61,0.3);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .membership-banner::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="50" height="50" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="25" cy="25" r="15" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/></svg>');
      background-size: 50px 50px;
    }
    
    .membership-banner > * {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .membership-banner .price {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--mint);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    /* Financial table with color */
    .financial-table {
      margin: 3rem 0;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    
    .financial-table table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    
    .financial-table thead {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pink) 0%, var(--coral) 100%);
      color: white;
    }
    
    .financial-table th {
      padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: left;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .financial-table td {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,107,157,0.1);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
    
    .financial-table tbody tr {
      background: white;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .financial-table tbody tr:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,107,157,0.05) 0%, white 100%);
      transform: scale(1.01);
    }
    
    .financial-table tbody tr:nth-child(n+3) {
      background: #FFF8F3;
    }
    
    .financial-table tbody tr:nth-child(n+3):hover {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,142,114,0.1) 0%, #FFF8F3 100%);
    }
    
    .financial-table td:first-child {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--dark);
    }
    
    .financial-table .margin {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--pink);
    }
    
    /* Team section with photos */
    .team-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(450px, 1fr));
      gap: 3rem;
      margin: 4rem 0;
    }
    
    .team-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 3rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .team-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      right: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,107,157,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
      transition: all 0.5s ease;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    
    .team-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 70px rgba(255,107,157,0.2);
    }
    
    .team-card:hover::before {
      opacity: 1;
      top: -20%;
      right: -20%;
    }
    
    .team-header {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .founder-photo {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 5px solid transparent;
      background: linear-gradient(white, white) padding-box,
                  linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pink), var(--lavender)) border-box;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255,107,157,0.3);
    }
    
    .team-info h3 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--dark);
    }
    
    .team-info .role {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--pink);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .team-card .body-text {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }
    
    /* Why we win cards */
    .win-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
    }
    
    .win-card {
      background: white;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      border-top: 5px solid var(--pink);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .win-card:nth-child(2) { border-top-color: var(--coral); }
    .win-card:nth-child(3) { border-top-color: var(--lavender); }
    .win-card:nth-child(4) { border-top-color: var(--mint); }
    .win-card:nth-child(5) { border-top-color: var(--peach); }
    .win-card:nth-child(6) { border-top-color: var(--pink); }
    
    .win-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(255,107,157,0.2);
    }
    
    .win-card h4 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--dark);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .win-card p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    
    /* Final statement box */
    .statement-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pink) 0%, var(--lavender) 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 4rem 3rem;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 4rem 0;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 60px rgba(255,107,157,0.3);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    
    /* Closing section */
    .closing {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark) 0%, #2A1A3D 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .closing::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="80" height="80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="40" cy="40" r="20" fill="rgba(255,107,157,0.1)"/></svg>');
      background-size: 80px 80px;
      animation: float 25s linear infinite;
    }
    
    .closing h2 {
      font-size: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .closing .wave-divider {
      width: 500px;
      max-width: 80%;
      height: 50px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="500" height="50" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M0 25 Q 125 10, 250 25 T 500 25" stroke="rgba(127,255,218,0.8)" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/></svg>') center/contain no-repeat;
    }
    
    .raise-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 3.5rem;
      border-radius: 25px;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }
    
    .raise-box h3 {
      color: var(--mint);
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .raise-box p {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    
    .contact-box {
      background: rgba(255,107,157,0.2);
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .contact-box h4 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: white;
    }
    
    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .team-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      
      .team-header {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      section {
        padding: 3rem 0;
      }
      
      .stats-grid,
      .win-grid,
      .tracks-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
    
    /* Scroll reveal */
    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: all 0.8s ease;
    }
    
    .reveal.active {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Jane</h1>

This represents a <span class="highlight-coral">₦3.3 trillion annual market</span>, spanning libido-enhancing supplements, birth control, fertility-boosting products, and weight-loss medications.</p>
      
      <p class="body-text">The taboo does not suppress demand. Instead, it <span class="highlight-pink">pushes demand out of formal healthcare systems</span>.</p>
      
      <p class="body-text">Today, many women rely on Instagram vendors and informal online sellers rather than hospitals, clinics, or licensed pharmacies. This has resulted in:</p>

  <script>
    // Scroll reveal animation
    function reveal() {
      const reveals = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
      
      reveals.forEach(element => {
        const windowHeight = window.innerHeight;
        const elementTop = element.getBoundingClientRect().top;
        const elementVisible = 150;
        
        if (elementTop < windowHeight - elementVisible) {
          element.classList.add('active');
        }
      });
    }
    
    window.addEventListener('scroll', reveal);
    reveal(); // Check on load
  </script>
